TRON2 MuJoCo simulator
Copyright (c) 2024-2026 LimX Dynamics Inc.

This product contains a Python MuJoCo-based simulator (`simulator.py`) that
bridges the LimX low-level SDK (`RobotCmd` / `RobotState`, with q / dq / tau /
Kp / Kd) to a MuJoCo `MjModel` / `MjData` simulation of the TRON2A humanoid
platform, together with the accompanying documentation and media.

